Privacy Policy for Luxan App
Effective Date: 24th February, 2025

Luxan App ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our services.

1. Information We Collect
When you use Luxan App, we may collect the following types of information:

Personal Information: Name, email address, profile picture (collected when signing in via Google, Facebook, or email).
Usage Data: App interactions, preferences, and in-app activities.
Device Information: Device type, operating system, app version, and IP address.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:

Provide and improve our services.
Authenticate users via Google Sign-In or other methods.
Ensure security, prevent fraud, and comply with legal obligations.
3. Sharing Your Information
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties. However, we may share it with:

Service Providers: Such as Firebase for authentication and analytics.
Legal Authorities: If required by law.
4. Data Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no online service is 100% secure.

5. Your Rights
You have the right to:

Access, update, or delete your personal information.
Withdraw consent for data collection.
Request a copy of your data.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy. We will notify you of major changes via email or app notifications.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions, contact us at Abdulazizkoroma6@gmail.com.
